    <div class="boxed">
        <h3>SMART ENOUGH TO KNOW BETTER.</h3> 
        <p> 
        Your best opportunity for success in any situation is to have 
        access to the highest level of knowledge and a thorough understanding 
        of how to make the most of it. At Revolution Systems, we design, 
        develop and maintain complex software systems that work &mdash; and 
        we show you how to make them work for you. You see, while we're 
        experts in the deployment of large web applications, we're also 
        specialists in making them easy to understand &mdash; from the 
        first line of code to launch day and beyond. 
        </p> 
    </div>
       
    <div class="boxed">
         
        <h3><a href="/services/django/">Django</a></h3> 
        <p> 
        <strong>A LITTLE KNOWLEDGE CAN BE DANGEROUS.</strong> 
        What you don't know can hurt you, so we offer expert Django 
        <a href="/training/">training</a>, <a href="/services/django/">commercial support</a>, consulting and development services. 
        Our unparalleled insight and understanding of Django makes us 
        the best provider for the support you'll need to make application 
        writing fast and easy.
        </p> 
    </div>

    <div class="boxed">
         
        <h3>INFRASTRUCTURE/DEPLOYMENT</h3> 
        <strong>THE VALUE OF APPLIED KNOWLEDGE.</strong> 
        <p> 
        Our experience places us in a position to do more for you than 
        handle infrastructure scaling, performance and deployment. 
        We're always available to handle maintenance and updates while 
        continuing to work with your people. More than a resource, 
        we're the source for software development, system administration 
        and Open Source software support.
        </p> 
        <p> 
        What does that mean to you and your company? It means you have 
        all the extra help &mdash; make that <em>expert</em> help &mdash; 
        whenever you need it without the extra staff. And your people will 
        learn from us while still being free to devote themselves to what 
        they do best. Our customized systems deliver value by helping you 
        work smarter and reduce costs.
        </p> 
    </div>

    <div class="boxed"> 
        <h3><a href="/services/postgresql/">PostgreSQL</a></h3> 
        <strong>SECURE IN THE KNOWLEDGE.</strong> 
        <p> 
        Because PostgreSQL is the world's most advanced Open Source SQL 
        database system, you need to be sure about who you trust for 
        performance tuning and support. No one's more qualified to show you 
        how to maximize your database server and take full advantage of this 
        exceptional and affordable system. 
        </p> 
    </div> 
     
